room_title: Escape room "Dive To Atlantis!" by The Escape Artist in Seattle
review: Wow!!!  Amazing!  This was an amazing experience. The puzzle makers thought of everything. We did the Atlantis room which was difficult but a lot of fun. I don't want to reveal too much but just when you think you made it back to the surface safely, think again.Everyone working there was very nice and a lot of fun.Thank you for creating something so immersive and interesting!!
